        "id": 5145
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-03-26T19:04:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Minutes might be nice to have for people who want to do stuff like 5:30-10:30 or something. Should definitely never need seconds though, we probably cannot guarantee that level of accuracy either. Could simplify things a little by removing support.\n\nAlso removing support for Day1-Day5 ranges would also simplify things but upto you.",
      "parentUuid": "08acfe2a_e0c29375",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 1,
